{"tid":767584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【詭異挖墳】傷心父為夭折兒開棺驚見膠公仔 揭女友扮大肚防佢變心","createTime":"2018-08-04T15:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T03:32:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf6b856236bd760a39a504eab8bfeefce211aed","tid":767584,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:53:00.000Z","msg":"洪都拉斯一名父親為夭折的寶寶舉行葬禮後覺得事有蹺蹊，決定到墳地挖棺一查究竟，誰知打開棺木一看，驚見內裡躺著的只是一個嬰兒塑膠公仔，揭發女友假裝懷孕九個月再假稱寶寶夭折，全因避免他變心。<br />\n<br />\n被騙男子門多薩（Melvin Mendoza）是一名軍人，女友迪亞茲（Rosa Castellanos Diaz）9個月前假裝懷上雙胞胎，至上周五迪亞茲獨自離村前往首都特古西加爾巴（Tegucigalpa），聲稱是前往醫院誕子，迪亞茲當晚打電話給門多薩告知「噩耗」，稱其中一名寶寶在誕下後死亡，門多薩及家人傷心不已，只好按傳統為寶寶守靈，並等待迪亞茲帶同死去的嬰兒回村。<br />\n<br />\n迪亞茲翌日歸來時帶同一副白棺木，她聲稱醫院早已封棺，並嚴禁她打開查看，眾人只好就此為亡嬰舉行葬禮。門多薩當時未有起疑，親手將「骨肉」埋入黃土。<br />\n<br />\n然而門多薩多名友人都覺得迪亞茲的說法有可疑，懷疑她說謊欺騙門多薩，於是眾人又陪同門多薩一起去「挖棺」查探。其中一名陪同挖棺的友人梅希亞（Ismael Mejia）稱：「整件事甚為不妥，所以我們晚上就到墳場將棺木挖起。當我們打開棺木時，驚見內裡是個公仔，並穿上嬰孩的服裝。」片段見到，白棺木在夜晚十分搶眼，打開後有人用電筒照入棺內的塑膠公仔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/235243_0f5d279e6f3a9a65cde91a405822b659.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F235243_0f5d279e6f3a9a65cde91a405822b659.png&h=b27a00e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/235243_49be3a742eab1724d0d1461ec005b099.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F235243_49be3a742eab1724d0d1461ec005b099.png&h=0c593fc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180804/58517897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58517897&d=lfJ9k9yE%2BQUrFpGwk%2Frh0AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=40fb2da0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58517897&h=34846efc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180804/58517897</a>"},{"pid":"a50dd6e612cf6d09ec0010b5eb73e1192e5c97cc","tid":767584,"uid":91931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"個FD都夠膽<br />\n如果係真會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea7f075a668ac78a619e71f1aeb6e1d3639742b","tid":767584,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"見到個公仔好似仲恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e53ba1a3ccf24fbc1b66d3a23faf001c4521889","tid":767584,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea0599e96ace644c3ecd668cdb0b60958fb5113","tid":767584,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"bb 來了個公仔"},{"pid":"1a830241ae15ce0d28887c1417d3c2398687139e","tid":767584,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:21:00.000Z","msg":"點瞞到九個月咁犀利"},{"pid":"4407b97fb8e9a02b4dd791cea0babd644946156a","tid":767584,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:21:45.000Z","msg":"又話雙胞胎 另一個點呃"},{"pid":"3f87fe0e115db7960fea991adde19f5a3ae2b440","tid":767584,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:30:30.000Z","msg":"娃鬼回魂<br />\n咁又放左佢出黎 又要拍多一集"},{"pid":"6b8a90a9c255dcef182daf90ac833f8d09acf7db","tid":767584,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T17:35:38.000Z","msg":"洪都拉斯咁玩法真係小心命都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c613f551af4e486eaaaf3688e2949035544bbb","tid":767584,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e53ba1a3ccf24fbc1b66d3a23faf001c4521889","tid":767584,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc